            while True:
                if char != "c":
                    break
                else:
                    count += 1
                    char = input_list[count]
            if count % 4 == 0:

Note that this solution assumes that there are no other characters in the input list besides "c". If there are other characters, they will be ignored and only "c" will be processed.
